    </p>
    <p>
      Dr. Kraker is Board Certified in Psychiatry and Neurology. In addition to her Adult Psychiatry training at Weil Cornell University, she has a graduate degree in Human Nutrition from Columbia College of Physicians and Surgeons, and studied nutritional epigenetics as a Psychiatric Epidemiology Fellow at the Mailman School of Public Health.
    </p>
